306 Woods Ferry Road, Highway 109, Lebanon, TN
Black and white photograph of stone cornerstone in stone wall reading "Andrews Tabernacle of the C.M.E.C. erected by G. L. Davis Pastor Oct 17, 1897"
Andrews Tabernacle Christian Methodist Episicopal Church was established in 1897.
